 *  constructed from generator (HepMC) particles ( HepMC::GenParticle )
 *
 *  @see LoKi_HepMCParticleMaker
 *
 *  This file is a part of LoKi project - 
 *    "C++ ToolKit  for Smart and Friendly Physics Analysis"
